  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they say to pinch the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] they used to call them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they used to put them in-- you know, we used to have in the block, we used to have a little stove.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to put them there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A stove?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it's a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to have there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they used to put the potatoes to-- to--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To cook.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To toast them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- my two legs, they were sticking already from the hunger there was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to say to my friend Victoria, I say, I'm going to pinch that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to-- because if you didn't pinch, you will die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we pinched the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We give them one each.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they came to look for them-- but they were fed still, because they used to work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we took them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You mean the Polish ladies?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish lady.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we ate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, oh, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Italians, they pinched the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], they used to tell us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], we used to say to them, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after, we became friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because everybody there-- you didn't care if it was your mother or father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you were hungry, you could kill your father to pinch the-- the bread to eat, you see.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So another time, we were so cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw another lady died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We say, we take the blouse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we want to take the blouse, inside here in the thing, there were so many [INAUDIBLE], [NON-ENGLISH], you know, all the-- Fleas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but they were [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the ticks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Full up, because they didn't wash themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe they were dying from the sickness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
